beer.beer_description:
Pacific Haze draws
inspiration from
enjoying a cold beer
while overlooking our
majestic Pacific Ocean.
Lovingly brewed with
Australian malt and our
favourite hops from
Oceania, pouring a
delicate yellow haze
with an abundance of
tropical fruit flavours
and a refreshing crisp
finish!

That's 75 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 16!

items.badge_description: Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 70 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 15! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.badge_description: There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 25 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 6!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 25 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 6!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 10 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 3!

items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 50 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 11!
Ahh, the trusty pale ale; crisp, refreshing, and always a good choice in a bind. That's 10 different Pale Ales or American Pale Wheats. Try 5 more for Level 3.

items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now its time to drink it! That's 290 check-ins with a photo.  Try 5 more for Level 59!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 260 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 53!

items.checkin_comment: Footy finals beer. 4 pack went down easy before third quarter. Fruity and made in Brisbane to support the Brisbane Lions in the AFL final.
